title: Who’s Making the Leap in 2021?
description:
Kevin and Nora are joined by The Ringer’s Danny Kelly and Establish the Run's Evan Silva to discuss which players and teams they think are going to take a step forward in 2021 (4:08).

Hosts: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
Guests: Danny Kelly and Evan Silva
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
